@InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:5001

### Locations — get configured list
GET {{InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress}}/api/locations
Accept: application/json

###

### Locations — update list
PUT {{InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress}}/api/locations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": [
    "London",
    "Birmingham",
    "Leeds",
    "Manchester",
    "Sheffield",
    "Bradford",
    "Liverpool",
    "Bristol"
  ]
}

###

### Scrape — all configured locations
POST {{InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress}}/api/scrape
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Scrape — selected locations only
POST {{InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress}}/api/scrape
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "locations": ["London", "Liverpool"]
}

###

### Solicitors — all stored contacts
GET {{InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress}}/api/solicitors
Accept: application/json

###

### Solicitors — filter by locations
GET {{InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress}}/api/solicitors?locations=London,Liverpool
Accept: application/json

###

### Report — summary
GET {{InfoTrack.SolicitorScraper.Api_HostAddress}}/api/reports/summary
Accept: application/json

###